If you're feeling super wedded to the routines and rules right now, you can definitely still follow them. Some people really find a sense of comfort and control in following a specific plan or rules around food.&#x20;

You might also find it helpful to take the chat app off your phone for the time being if it’s causing you quite a bit of tension and panic. **Your body and your health are unique to you, and what works for someone else might not work for you.** Try and practice as much patience and kindness with yourself as you can, even if it's hard feeling like you're struggling.

This could be getting repetitive so a change of environment is important. Consider something new for a bit, like a new hike or listening to a new CD—try and broaden your horizons with different tree names or types of mountain flowers.&#x20;
